Rule of Thumb for Byte Order
============================

For hex strings, assume they are in RPC order (i.e. reverse order to the intuitive one).
For binary arrays, assume they are in little endian order.

Big transaction generation
==========================

See https://live.blockcypher.com/btc-testnet/tx/637fc5cf6351c19296d7ac92fce21f16a59388622389e01c7dac556481c8cb50/ for an example.
